quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  10,26,"Hino woodani Й“en moЖґЖґimЙ“e (golle) moЖґЖґere e Й“eydaari. Nduggu hippataa geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, wanaa kadi koyeera. Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton"
  10,27,"ЖЃen faggitiiЙ“e boneeji Й—in, njoЙ“di bone ko yeru makko. Koyeera hippay Й“e, Alanaa Й“e immorde ka Alla hay daЙ—ndoowo, A sikkay geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko hippiraa ko taЖґontinnde jemma niЙ“Й“utuЙ—o. Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Yiite, kamЙ“e ko luttooЙ“e ton"
  10,28,"Г‘alnde Men mooЙ“indirta Й“e denndaangal, refti Men wi'ana Й“en sirkunooЙ“e : \"Wonee e nokku mon, onon e kafidiiЙ“e mon.\" Men senndindira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, kafidiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'a : \"Wonaa menen wonunoЙ—on e rewude"
  10,29,"Alla yonii seedee hakkunde amen e mon. Si ko woni, men laatinoke welsindiiЙ“e gaay e dewe mon Й—en"
  10,30,Ko Й—on wonkii kala jarriborte ko ki ardinnoo. ЖЃe ruttitee ka Alla GiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on ka goonga; ko Й“e wonunoo fefindaande kon majjira Й“e
  10,31,"Maaku : \"Ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Kaa ko hommbo jeyti nanЙ—e Й—en e giiЙ—e Й—en, ko hommbo kadi yaltinta ko wuuri e nder ko maayi, o yaltina ka maayi e nder ko wuuri, ko hommbo kadi yiilata fiyaaku on?\" ЖЃe wi'ay : \"Ko Alla\". Maaku : \"E on hulatah"
  10,32,"Ko on Й—on mo'on Alla, woni jeyЙ—o on e goonga. Ko honЙ—um woni Й“aawo goonga si wanaa majjere? Ko honno firlitirte Й—on"
  10,33,"Ko wano nii konngol Joomi maa ngol jojjiri e hoore faasiqinЙ“e Й“en :wonnde pellet, Й“e gomЙ—intah"
